Package us.ullberg.startpunkt.objects.kubernetes

Class AnnotatedKubernetesObject

java.lang.Object
us.ullberg.startpunkt.objects.kubernetes.BaseKubernetesObject
us.ullberg.startpunkt.objects.kubernetes.AnnotatedKubernetesObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
KubernetesObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
GatewayApiHttpRouteWrapper, IngressApplicationWrapper, IstioVirtualServiceApplicationWrapper, RouteApplicationWrapper
public abstract class AnnotatedKubernetesObject extends BaseKubernetesObject
Abstract base class for Kubernetes objects that extract application properties from annotations. Extends BaseKubernetesObject and overrides methods to get app info from Kubernetes resource annotations.
